)attr default(%+_)
  _ type( input) intens(low ) just(left ) hilite(uscore)
  ~ type(text) intens(high) caps(off) just(asis ) hilite(reverse) color(turq)
  Ý type(output) intens(high) caps(off) just(left) pas(on)
)Body Expand(\\)
%Tutorial -\-\~The z ISPF Git Interface (zigi)%\-\- Tutorial
%Selection ===>_ZCMD                                                          +
+
                          %Menus and the Action Bar
+
+Using point-and-shoot capabilities works well with zigi. Double-click anywhere
+outside the table and a pop-up menu appears with point-and-shoot selections.
+Double-click within the table and a popup appears for row selection options for
+that specific row.
+
+The F3 below the Scroll field may be used as a point-and-shoot field to invoke
+the F3 (End) command.
+
+The action bar is also available for command selections.
+
+
+
+ "If no mistake you have made, losing you are. A different game
+     you should play."    -- Master Yoda
+
+
          +Press the%Enter+key to continue your ZIGI tutorial journey.
)Init
 .cursor = &zcmd
)PROC
 &zcont = zigih030
)END
